> d 2026-04-30)
>          (this is a `do'-scope script — needs its own macros_va include for l
> ocals)
>       - All LEGACY `$vaprojdir/data/...' reads preserved (restricted-access K
> 12 +
>         crosswalks per ADR-0017; static run-time inputs).
